{
  "__inputs": [],
  "__requires": [
    { "type": "grafana", "id": "grafana", "name": "Grafana", "version": "10.0.0" },
    { "type": "datasource", "id": "prometheus", "name": "Prometheus", "version": "1.0.0" }
  ],
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "description": "WAF (ModSecurity / nginx) edge security metrics — connections, request rate, exporter health, and audit log guidance.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "WAF Exporter Health",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "text": "UP", "color": "green" } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DOWN", "color": "red" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "up{job=\"waf\"}",
          "legendFormat": "WAF exporter",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Active Connections",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 50 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 200 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "nginx_connections_active{job=\"waf\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Active",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Waiting / Reading / Writing Connections",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "nginx_connections_waiting{job=\"waf\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Waiting",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "nginx_connections_reading{job=\"waf\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Reading",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "nginx_connections_writing{job=\"waf\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Writing",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Request Rate (req/s through WAF)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "rate(nginx_http_requests_total{job=\"waf\"}[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "Requests/s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Active Connections Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "nginx_connections_active{job=\"waf\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Active",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "nginx_connections_accepted{job=\"waf\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Accepted (cumulative)",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "WAF Audit Log — How to inspect blocked requests",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "options": {
        "content": "## ModSecurity Audit Log\n\nBlocked requests are written as JSON to `/var/log/modsec_audit.log` inside the WAF pod.\n\n**Inspect live:**\n```sh\nkubectl exec -n ai-gateway deploy/waf -c waf -- tail -f /var/log/modsec_audit.log\n```\n\n**Count blocked requests:**\n```sh\nkubectl exec -n ai-gateway deploy/waf -c waf -- grep -c '\"action\"' /var/log/modsec_audit.log\n```\n\n**Test a SQLi attack (should return 403):**\n```sh\ncurl -i 'http://localhost/?id=1%27+OR+%271%27%3D%271'\n```\n\n**Pod health:**\n```sh\nkubectl get pod -n ai-gateway -l app=waf\nkubectl logs -n ai-gateway deploy/waf -c waf --tail=40\n```",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "tags": ["waf", "security", "edge", "modsecurity"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "WAF Edge Security",
  "uid": "waf-edge-security",
  "version": 1
}
